import { Field } from '../types';
import isUndefined from '../utils/isUndefined';

export default (
  value: any,
  { valueAsNumber, valueAsDate, setValueAs }: Field['_f'],
) =>
  isUndefined(value)
    ? value
    : valueAsNumber
    ? value === ''
      ? NaN
      : +value
    : valueAsDate
    ? new Date(value)
    : setValueAs
    ? setValueAs(value)
    : value;

import { RegisterOptions } from '../types';

export default <T extends RegisterOptions>(options?: T, mounted?: boolean) =>
  mounted &&
  options &&
  (options.required ||
    options.min ||
    options.max ||
    options.maxLength ||
    options.minLength ||
    options.pattern ||
    options.validate);
